                <spanspec namest="1" nameend="4" spanname="S1T4"/>
                <tbody>
                    <row>
                        <entry colspan="4" spanname="S1T4">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">Connector V Ref Voltage Checks</emph>
                            </para>
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">(If multiple faults set remove and measure V Ref at suspected sensor
                                    circuits)
                                </emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>Sensor</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>Test Points</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3">
                            <para>Spec.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4">
                            <para>Comments</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>ICP</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>B to Grd.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3">
                            <para>5 &#177; .5 v</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4" morerows="2">
                            <para>Check V Ref as suspected sensors on at a time. Identifying which sensors do not have V
                                Ref and which ones share common V Ref feed will more quickly help isolate the area of a
                                short or open circuit.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
